<article id="post-906" class="post-906 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-the-bookering category-volume-ii-print">
	
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h1 class="entry-title">Volume II illustrations.</h1>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>OK, here is my Volume II in pictures. It came out as a sort of a story. What you think?<br />
<span id="more-906"></span><br />
<strong>Stop</strong> <figure id="attachment_908" style="width: 300px;" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/1-stop.jpg"><img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/1-stop.jpg?w=300" alt="" title="Stop" width="300" height="300" class="size-medium wp-image-908" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">&quot;Do you remember love?&quot;</figcaption></figure></p>
<p><strong>Ghost</strong> <figure id="attachment_909" style="width: 300px;" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/2-ghost.jpg"><img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/2-ghost.jpg?w=300" alt="" title="Ghost" width="300" height="300" class="size-medium wp-image-909" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">&quot;I have been here for so long that my memories are fading.&quot;</figcaption></figure></p>
<p><strong>Gone</strong> <figure id="attachment_910" style="width: 298px;" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/3-gone.jpg"><img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/3-gone.jpg?w=298" alt="" title="Gone" width="298" height="300" class="size-medium wp-image-910" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">&quot;I like this world a lot more with its people gone.&quot;</figcaption></figure></p>
<p><strong>Outsider</strong> <figure id="attachment_911" style="width: 300px;" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/4-outsider.jpg"><img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/4-outsider.jpg?w=300" alt="" title="Outsider" width="300" height="298" class="size-medium wp-image-911" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">&quot;An irregular section of the wall swung back. &quot;</figcaption></figure></p>
<p><strong>Cat</strong> <figure id="attachment_912" style="width: 295px;" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/5-cat.jpg"><img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/5-cat.jpg?w=295" alt="" title="Cat" width="295" height="300" class="size-medium wp-image-912" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">‚ÄúExamine, ye, my untouchable beauty.‚Äù </figcaption></figure></p>
<p><strong>Eye</strong> <figure id="attachment_913" style="width: 297px;" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/6-eye.jpg"><img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/6-eye.jpg?w=297" alt="" title="Eye" width="297" height="300" class="size-medium wp-image-913" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">‚ÄúI like it. It helps me concentrate.‚Äù </figcaption></figure></p>
<p><strong>Subterfuge</strong> <figure id="attachment_907" style="width: 300px;" class="wp-caption alignnone"><a href="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/7-subterfuge.jpg"><img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2011/04/7-subterfuge.jpg?w=300" alt="" title="Subterfuge" width="300" height="298" class="size-medium wp-image-907" /></a><figcaption class="wp-caption-text"> ‚Äú‚Ä¶he looked back at me, confused but not afraid, before he was taken.‚Äù </figcaption></figure></p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	
